        <div style="font-size:.65rem;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--green);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid #1a4030;">⚡ 특이 기록</div>
